# FreeCodeCamp Survey Form Project

![HTML5](https://img.shields.io/badge/HTML5-E34F26?style=flat&logo=html5&logoColor=white)
![CSS3](https://img.shields.io/badge/CSS3-1572B6?style=flat&logo=css3&logoColor=white)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Completed-brightgreen)
![FreeCodeCamp](https://img.shields.io/badge/FreeCodeCamp-Responsive%20Web%20Design-orange)
![Tests](https://img.shields.io/badge/Tests-44%2F44%20Passed-success)

A responsive survey form about favorite movies built to meet all 44 FreeCodeCamp test requirements. This project demonstrates HTML form structure, CSS styling, input validation, and responsive design principles through a movie-themed survey interface.

---

## üìñ Project Description

Build a survey form that is functionally similar to the FreeCodeCamp example, implementing all required user stories for form elements, validation, styling, and accessibility. The form collects user information about their favorite movies including personal details, genre preferences, theater experience, and snack choices.

### FreeCodeCamp Requirements Met ‚úÖ
- **44/44 tests passed** - All user stories implemented correctly
- Form structure with proper IDs and semantic HTML
- Input validation and accessibility features
- Responsive design with custom styling
- Multiple input types and form controls

---

## üíª Implementation Breakdown

### **HTML Structure (index.html)**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Survey Form</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1 id="title">Survey Form</h1>
    <p id="description">Favorite Movie</p>
    <form method="POST" id="survey-form">
      <!-- Form content with all required elements -->
    </form>
  </body>
</html>
```

### **CSS Styling (styles.css)**
```css
body {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100vh;
  margin: 0;
  background-color: #271F30;
  color: #D0FCB3;
  font-family: Tahoma;
  font-size: 16px;
}

/* Responsive form design with custom dark theme */
```

---

## üéØ Form Elements & Validation

### **Personal Information Section**
- **Name Field** (`id="name"`): Required text input with placeholder
- **Email Field** (`id="email"`): Required email input with HTML5 validation
- **Age Field** (`id="number"`): Number input with min="15" max="120" constraints

### **Movie Preferences Section**
- **Genre Dropdown** (`id="dropdown"`): 8 movie genre options
- **Movie Name**: Required text input for favorite movie title
- **Theater Experience**: Radio button group (Yes/No)
- **Snack Choices**: Multiple checkboxes (Pizza, Popcorn, Peanut M&M's, Twizzlers)
- **Snack Explanation**: Textarea for detailed response

### **Form Controls**
- **Submit Button** (`id="submit"`): Proper form submission handling
- **Fieldset Organization**: Logical grouping with proper legends
- **Label Association**: All inputs properly labeled for accessibility

---

## üé® Design & Styling Features

### **Color Scheme**
- **Background**: `#271F30` (Dark purple theme)
- **Text**: `#D0FCB3` (Light green for readability)
- **Input Fields**: `#0a0a23` (Dark blue backgrounds)
- **Submit Button**: `#3b3b4f` (Medium gray with white border)
- **Accent Borders**: `#6457A6` (Purple fieldset separators)

### **Responsive Design**
- **Form Width**: 60vw with 500px maximum width
- **Centered Layout**: Auto margins for horizontal centering
- **Flexible Inputs**: 100% width with proper spacing
- **Mobile-First**: Viewport meta tag for mobile responsiveness

### **Typography & Spacing**
- **Font Family**: Tahoma for clean readability
- **Base Font Size**: 16px for accessibility
- **Input Height**: Minimum 2em for touch targets
- **Form Padding**: 2em bottom spacing

---

## ‚úÖ FreeCodeCamp Test Requirements

### **Required Elements (Tests 1-18)**
- ‚úÖ H1 with `id="title"` containing text
- ‚úÖ P element with `id="description"` containing text
- ‚úÖ Form with `id="survey-form"`
- ‚úÖ Name input with `id="name"`, `type="text"`, required
- ‚úÖ Email input with `id="email"`, `type="email"`, required
- ‚úÖ Number input with `id="number"`, `type="number"`, min/max attributes

### **Labels & Accessibility (Tests 19-30)**
- ‚úÖ Labels with IDs: `name-label`, `email-label`, `number-label`
- ‚úÖ Descriptive label text for all inputs
- ‚úÖ Proper form nesting for all labeled elements
- ‚úÖ Placeholder attributes with meaningful values

### **Form Controls (Tests 31-44)**
- ‚úÖ Select dropdown with `id="dropdown"` and multiple options
- ‚úÖ Radio button groups with proper `name` attributes
- ‚úÖ Multiple checkboxes with `value` attributes
- ‚úÖ Textarea for additional comments
- ‚úÖ Submit button with `id="submit"` and `type="submit"`

